OL,3,CEuropean ski resorts face 'existential
OL,4,Cthreat' due to climate change
OL,6,FEuropean ski resorts face an
OL,7,F"existential threat" due to climate
OL,8,Fchange, experts have warned.
OL,10,FThe World Meteorological Organisation
OL,11,F(WMO) and the International Ski (FIS)
OL,12,Fsaid winter sports and tourism face a
OL,13,Fbleak future due to rising
OL,14,Ftemperatures, as they announced a new
OL,15,Fpartnership to promote change.
