OL,3,CEuropean ski resorts face 'existential
OL,4,Cthreat' due to climate change
OL,6,FResearch shows the "zero-degree level"
OL,7,F- the altitude where the temperature
OL,8,Fis zero and therefore allows lasting
OL,9,Fsnow - could rise from 850 metres to
OL,10,F1,500 metres by 2060 if no action is
OL,11,Ftaken, according to the Swiss Climate
OL,12,FChange Scenarios.
OL,14,FThis means resorts that extend lower
OL,15,Fthan 1,500 metres could face dramatic
OL,16,Fchanges to their slopes and could mean
OL,17,Fthey need to increasingly rely on
OL,18,Fartificial snow.
