OL,6,FFIS President, Johan Eliasch, said:
OL,7,F"The climate crisis is obviously far
OL,8,Fbigger than FIS  or sports, for that
OL,9,Fmatter: it is a genuine crossroads for
OL,10,Fmankind.
OL,12,F"It is true, though, that climate
OL,13,Fchange is, simply put, an existential
OL,14,Fthreat to skiing and snowboarding."
