OL,3,CEuropean ski resorts face 'existential
OL,4,Cthreat' due to climate change
OL,6,FA report by Nature Climate Change in
OL,7,F2023 projects that over half of
OL,8,FEurope's ski resorts will face a
OL,9,Fsevere lack of snow if temperatures
OL,10,Frise 2 degrees Celsius above pre-
OL,11,Findustrial levels - while nearly all
OL,12,Fwould be at high risk by an increase
OL,13,Fof 4 degrees.
OL,15,FNot only do changes in snowfall and
OL,16,Fsnow cover have an effect on winter
OL,17,Ftourism, but it also impacts
OL,18,Fhydropower and transport.
