OL,3,CEuropean ski resorts face 'existential
OL,4,Cthreat' due to climate change
OL,6,FIn Switzerland, alpine glaciers have
OL,7,Flost about 60% of their volume since
OL,8,F1850, according to MeteoSwiss.
OL,10,FThey also found that the number of
OL,11,Fdays with snowfall at altitudes below
OL,12,F800 metres has halved since 1970.
OL,14,FIn October, the Swiss government
OL,15,Fannounced that part of the border
OL,16,Fbetween Italy and Switzerland is set
OL,17,Fto be redrawn as the glaciers that
OL,18,Fmark the boundary are melting.
